## üé® Optional CSS Additions

Add these extra styles to your existing `css/style.css` (just scroll to the bottom and paste):

```css
.about {
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.about-img {
  width: 45%;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.about-text {
  flex: 1;
}

.about-text h2 {
  margin-top: 15px;
  color: var(--mocha);
}

.values {
  margin-top: 10px;
  list-style: square;
  padding-left: 20px;
  color: var(--coffee);
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
  }
}
```

